nodes.text: Skirmish in the Cavamina Minor cantina

A skirmish occurred in a cantina on Cavamina Minor around 22 BBY. The Jedi Knight Aayla Secura arrived at the cantina with an escort of clone troopers in search of the pirate Attuma Duum, but they were attacked by several operatives in Duum's employ. Secura was the only survivor of the ensuing lightfight.
